  "body": "Following on from: https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/16191\r\n\r\nAny of the quo2 components that are using `override-theme` prop need to be adjusted to use the with-theme HOC instead. \r\nThey're respective screens should also be updated too.\r\n\r\nIn the final state the code should get to the point where checks like `theme-color` and other theming utilitiy functions should always take `theme` as a parameter and there should be no direct checks on global ratoms etc.\r\n\r\nThis work can be split further if someone else wants to assist with the refactoring.",
